name: SomeNano
description: Building fun and useful apps in the Nano Ecosystem! My current portfolio of projects can be found at [SomeNano.com](https://somenano.com). Some highlights are my Nano Network visualizers [SomeNano Plinko](https://plinko.somenano.com) and [SomeNano Snow](https://snow.somenano.com). I also enjoy supporting community developers with [articles on Medium](https://somenano.medium.com) and dev tools like [Public Nodes](https://publicnodes.somenano.com).
